      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression and smooth double VANOS operation, while the chassis has been improved with essential rear subframe reinforcement. It retains a factory limited-slip differential for superior torque vectoring. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the suspension bushings are tight and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies remains razor-sharp. A mechanically sound, visceral performer for the purist.",
